SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT a.entity_id, a.navigation_id, b.Navigation_Name, b.Nav_URL
FROM valid_entity_navigations AS a INNER JOIN Navigations AS b ON a.navigation_id COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT = b.Navigation_ID COLLATE DATABASE_DEFAULT WHERE a.entity_id = :1 ORDER BY b.sort_order
select COUNT (DISTINCT entity_id ) from entity_property_value a, contact b where a.entity_id=b.contact_id and b.Contact_Parent_Id=:1 and a.property_classification=:2 :3 :4 :5 :6 :7 :8
select entity_id, posted_by, comment, date_posted, time_posted, stars, header, image from review where entity_id=:1 order by date_posted DESC, time_posted DESC
select count(*) from review where entity_id=:1
